    {
      "id": "36",
      "name": "更多訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "日常對話",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "「有什麼想聊的嗎？」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "喔，是妳/你啊。怎麼樣，想要找人聊聊天嗎？要不然我們邊打牌邊說吧...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話1：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "好啊，那就開始「七聖召喚」吧！",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利（玩家勝利）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "失敗的感覺還真是糟糕，就像是被不死之鳥啄走了驕傲一樣...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利（玩家失敗）：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "哈哈，我牌技並不好，所以偶爾這樣得勝一次還是滿開心的。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "對話2：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "暫時有別的事...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "馬克利：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "是嗎，那還真是可惜啊...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "七聖召喚",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "決鬥對局",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "關卡介紹",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "很喜歡打牌的須彌牌手，對「七聖召喚」的製作過程和來源瞭若指掌。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "【提示】這是一位強大的牌手，建議牌手等級高一些再來挑戰。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "對手陣容",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3196,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/292125737/348541b315d22c004cf91a87f4f5523e_6322174571484810552.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
